The firepower from Afterburner rips through the air towards Caliburst.
The Targetmaster has little time to think of what to do, as he tries to
repair Slusglinger's power relay to let him take off. The Firepower
smashes into him, sending him flying away from his down binary bonder,
as he lands on top of Tremor smoking.

"Caliburst, CALIBURST." Slugslinger screams in fear, although it is hard
to say if he is afraid for his partners safety, or his own now that he
can't transform. "I'll rip you a new tailpipe if he's hurt Autobots."
Slugslinger hisses in fury.

Grimlock stomps up to the Decepticon Jet. "Maybe in Inferno Decepticon."
he whispers, as he powers up another laser beam.

Cliffjumper sits up, "Yeah, i'll be okay." he looks to Pacifix, then
smiles. "Your a sight for sore eyes kid."

OOC: Actually jeff, they were all firing them while underwater attacking
the Decepticon headquarters, and again later, the Decepticon seekers
flew underwater firing missiles.
